Good Form.feedback: Correct: The shape of the vase clearly demonstrates craftsmanship.

Poor Taste.feedback: Wrong: Taste is in the eye of the designer as well as the viewer.

Contrasting Themes.feedback: Wrong: There is uniformity in the shape, but there is no depth to this media to imply that it is contrasting with other figures.

AI.feedback: Correct: While a modification of prior work, this is still AI generative work.

Shading.feedback: Wrong: While there is a light source and a shadow cast, shading is a term used for pencil based sketching.

Original Work.feedback: Wrong: Artwork created from gerenateive AI can not be original since it is trained on other artists work.

Accessible.feedback: Wrong: The color scheme while high contrast in some areas, loses form in others and has written text unrelated to the character.
